Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunter2 你为什么发动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunter2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在做什么 白银
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的话 或许还来得及
